headline.main: Donald Trump vs. the Food Snobs
headline.print_headline: Donald Trump vs. the Food Snobs

lead_paragraph: Kayla Goth scored a career-high 25, Eternati Willock had a double-double and No. 24 Kansas State made all 12 of its free throws in the last 1:11 to defeat Iowa State 74-67 in the Big 12 tournament quarterfinals on Saturday.
